{"tid":1656693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無大台就要靠大家各自努力","createTime":"2019-10-15T17:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T17:19:07.000Z","uid":234178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"682a2974c3757525c8b0989e53cddc2648e379d0","tid":1656693,"uid":234178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:18:24.000Z","msg":"最近多咗po指出某幾間大學「唔夠出位 恥與為伍」<br />\n例如 &quot;*大<span style=\"color: red;\">吹咗咁耐雞，現場只係得咁少人</span>&quot; &quot;*大<span style=\"color: red;\">同警犬係一個團體</span>&quot;<br />\n我發覺有人嘗試比較各個團體 抑或同對家聯上關係<br />\n恐怖嘅係呢啲po/ comment可以有唔少正皮<br />\n即使係對家打手 亦唔可以睇小風向對軍心嘅影響<br />\n<br />\n即使面對直接批評 甚至分化都要冷靜地一一面對<br />\n無論惡意分化定無心之失<br />\n矛頭始終如一 一致對外<br />\n<br />\n最後建議<strong>正視呢啲負面po背後想帶出嘅結論</strong><br />\n記得 不完美 <strong>可接受 要改善</strong><br />\n呢場運動之所以可以無大台 全靠大家嘅獨立思維 <br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力 sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"1ef0ac518ae0dcd7aba565c29a20005be7761b5e","tid":1656693,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC4rszp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdC4rszp.jpg&h=a54a4986&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6c84ed0b5625e216b71761208af91d692a37a060","tid":1656693,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F0WYmPf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF0WYmPf.jpg&h=e063d218&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d3a2b6b9471454e4116289ed05dbdf33ba71f22","tid":1656693,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T17:19:07.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n求幫推 p牌仔推唔喐<br />\n【簡易文宣】本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}